+.. NOTE::
+
+    The pattern for ``LIKE`` and ``ILIKE`` operators cannot end with the
+    ``ESCAPE`` character.
+
 Example of query with custom ESCAPE::

     cr> SELECT 'test' LIKE 'te%' escape 'e' as res;
